                源氏物语绘卷：“斜面－－等角透视”  ［美］鲁 阿尔海姆《艺术与视知觉》 1985 p386-387；
<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p33934267-1.jpg" alt="“SUZUMUSHI”"><br><span class="pic-title">“SUZUMUSHI”</span></div>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

